<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178247>
    dc:description "FIGURE 57. Facial marking pattern of Eustenogaster species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178247/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178244>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 – 45. Eustenogaster latebricola Saito, sp. nov.; 39, 41 – 45, holotype female. 40, paratype male. 39 – 40, second metasomal tergum in profile. 41 – 42, head; 41, frontal view and 42, lateral view. 43, ocelli. 44, lateral and dorsolateral furrows of pronotum. 45, first metasomal segment. Scale bars show 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178244/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178246>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 – 56. Eustenogaster spinicauda Saito, sp. nov.; 50, 52 – 54. 56, female holotype. 55 and 51, male paratype. 50, sixth metasomal tergum in lateral view. 51 – 53. 55, head; 52 and 55, frontal view, 51 and 53, lateral view. 54, ocelli. 56, second metasomal tergum in lateral view. Scale bars show 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178246/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178248>
    dc:description "FIGURE 58. Facial marking pattern of Eustenogaster species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178248/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178245>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46 – 49. 46 – 48, Eustenogaster latebricola Saito, sp. nov., male paratype. 49, E. eximia, female. 46 – 47, head; 46, frontal view and 47, lateral view. 48, ventroapical part of penis valve of aedeagus. 49, scutellum (SCL) and metanotum (MN) in lateral view. Scale bars show 1 mm except for fig. 48." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178245/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178249>
    dc:description "FIGURE 59. Male genitalia in Eustenogaster species. (A) E. gibbosa, in ventral view. (B – M) aedeagus in lateral view; (N – Y) vollsela with digitus in lateral view; (B, N) E. agilis; (C, O) E. fulvipennis; (D, P) E. fraterna; (E, Q) E. scitula; (F, R) E. calyptodoma; (G, S) E. gibbosa; (H, T) E. hauxwellii; (I, U) E. micans; (J, V) E. latebricola Saito, sp. nov.; (K, W) E. palavanica; (L, X) E. luzonensis; (M, Y) E. spinicauda Saito, sp. nov.." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178249/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

